raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Wwqq
Mabel: Thought: Babe.. what are you doing in my room?
Mabel: 111
Player: Is that a secret message? 😆
Mabel: sfx: bedcreak2: *creak*
Mabel: aaaaa
Mabel: Thought: It's okay you can sleep here
Mabel: Thought: But it's a little tight
Player: Did you fall asleep on your phone?
Player: It's been a while since you've done that lol
Mabel: img: mabel/125
- Waah gross 😆
	Player: Waah gross 😆
- Just a lil lower 👀
	Player: Just a lil lower 👀
Mabel: tnbs hj
Mabel: Thought: You're so warm silly
Mabel: PinkThought: I have to take off my PJs cause I'm sweating..
Mabel: sfx: bedcreak3: *creak*
Mabel: dbbbbb
Mabel: PinkThought: Promise not to look?
Player: Should I call you?
Mabel: 32qed2q
Mabel: PinkThought: I know you're peeking babe, I'm not a dummy
do heart(1)
do echo_set([\"126\"])
Mabel: PinkThought: Fine, only cause you're my boyfriend and I love you hehe
Mabel: sfx: breath4: Ughh...
Mabel: PinkThought: Hey don't touch me there silly
Mabel: PinkThought: At least be a little gentle hehe
Mabel: PinkThought: That feels really good..
Player: But that never wakes you up anyway lol
if Story.has_flag(\"Naomi1\")
	Mabel: PinkThought: Don't look at Naomi anymore hehe
	Mabel: PinkThought: I'll be extra cute just for you
Player: Okay well, good night then haha
do echo_clear()
Mabel: sfx: bedcreak4: *creak*
do heart(0)
Mabel: Thought: What's that light?
Mabel: Thought: Is someone messaging me?
Mabel: Baeb? I m slepping
Mabel: do u need somehing?
- What were you doing?
	Player: What were you doing?
	Mabel: What do you mean?
- You should get some sleep
	Player: You should get some sleep
	Mabel: I'm so sleepy
	Mabel: You too, but where did you go?
Mabel: You were just here?
Mabel: Thought: Wait, was I dreaming??
Mabel: Thought: Omg I was...
Mabel: PinkThought: And here I thought we... ugh gotta go through all that again
Player: Were you dreaming about me?
Mabel: WAS NOT 😶
Mabel: Thought: This is so embarassing!
Mabel: BYE!!
Player: Noo wait!
Player: Babe?? 🥲
=> END"
